OL,3,CGirl fitted with mechanical heart
OL,4,Ccould face two-year organ wait
OL,6,FThe parents of a girl who is being
OL,7,Fkept alive by a mechanical heart say
OL,8,Fthey face a potential two-year wait
OL,9,Ffor the transplant that would allow
OL,10,Fher to live a normal life.
OL,12,FFifteen-month-old Penelope Greathead,
OL,13,Ffrom Whitby, North Yorkshire, was
OL,14,Ftaken to Great Ormond Street Hospital
OL,15,Fin London last month to have a so-
OL,16,Fcalled "Berlin Heart" fitted.
OL,18,FThe machine is required to do the work
OL,19,Fof her heart after she suffered a
OL,20,Fcardiac arrest in November.
