OL,3,CGirl fitted with mechanical heart
OL,4,Ccould face two-year organ wait
OL,6,FBut Penelope, who was born with a
OL,7,Fcondition called dilated
OL,8,Fcardiomyopathy, is now waiting for a
OL,9,Fdonor of a similar age and size to
OL,10,Fprovide the heart she needs. She will
OL,11,Fbe confined to a hospital bed until an
OL,12,Forgan becomes available.
OL,14,FHer dad, Jordan, said: "She needs to
OL,15,Frecover from the operation that she's
OL,16,Fhad and be stable on the Berlin Heart.
OL,17,FAnd then from there it's (a case of)
OL,18,Fwaiting for the phone call to say
OL,19,Fthere's an organ available."
