OL,6,FPenelope's mum Hollie Suff added:
OL,7,F"Even though Penelope is on a Berlin
OL,8,FHeart and it's a fantastic device,
OL,9,Fthere's still a lot of risks that go
OL,10,Falong with it. There's a high risk of
OL,11,Fclotting that could potentially lead
OL,12,Fto a stroke, there's an infection
OL,13,Frisk. We're still on edge a lot and
OL,14,Fwe've been told we could wait up to
OL,15,Ftwo years for a transplant."
OL,17,FDespite being diagnosed with her heart
OL,18,Fcondition shortly after she was born,
OL,19,FPenelope was otherwise healthy until
OL,20,Fshe suffered a cardiac arrest during a
OL,21,Froutine medicine change.
