OL,6,FShe was on life support at Leeds
OL,7,FChildren Hospital while her family
OL,8,Fwaited for a place at Great Ormond
OL,9,FStreet.
OL,11,FMore than #125,000 was raised after a
OL,12,Fcampaign was launched to pay for a
OL,13,FBerlin Heart privately. The money will
OL,14,Fnow go to charity.
