OL,3,CGirl fitted with mechanical heart
OL,4,Ccould face two-year organ wait
OL,6,FJordan said she had responded well to
OL,7,Fthe treatment. He said: "The issue we
OL,8,Fhave at the moment is that because
OL,9,Fshe's been on so much sedation for so
OL,10,Flong she's dependent on it and they're
OL,11,Ftrying to wean it down slowly. But the
OL,12,Flast couple of days she's been really
OL,13,Fgood with it and she's coping with it
OL,14,Freally well."
OL,16,FThere are five children currently
OL,17,Ffitted with Berlin Hearts at Great
OL,18,FOrmond Street.
OL,20,FAlmost 40 children in the UK are
OL,21,Fwaiting for a heart transplant.
