OL,6,FPaediatric cardiologist Dr Matthew
OL,7,FFenton said: "The amount of time that
OL,8,Fwe need to support children in order
OL,9,Fto be transplanted has increased
OL,10,Fsignificantly from a few moths to a
OL,11,Fyear-and-a-half or so, which is a long
OL,12,Ftime for children to be waiting in a
OL,13,Fbed space on the high dependency unit."
OL,15,FPenelope's family are now appealing
OL,16,Ffor people to join the donor register.
