OL,6,FHollie said: "Even though we had a
OL,7,Fbaby with a heart condition, we never
OL,8,Fconsidered organ donation for our
OL,9,Fchild. Now we're in this world we can
OL,10,Fsee the huge benefit it could provide
OL,11,Fto other families, giving other
OL,12,Ffamilies a chance."
